Didn't owe a dollar. Not one dollar did we owe. Do 
you like the way that College Station has

33:03.121 --> 33:06.325
developed? The way you see it today? I'm not 
criticizing them at all. I think they're lucky

33:09.649 --> 33:11.771
that they didn't have me. I think they're awful 
lucky that they didn't have me because I didn't

33:18.503 --> 33:19.564
care. I wanted the school to grow, but I didn't care 
a thing about College Station growing other than

33:19.584 --> 33:28.732
just give room for the professors. I see. You 
wanted it to remain small, a small college town. A

33:33.897 --> 33:38.221
small college town, yeah.

